snippet.title: You Can't Scare Me - Game Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Scare or be scared in You Can't Scare Me - the VR haunted house where you can frighten your friends!  Set scary traps or transform into terrible monsters to try and scare the living daylights out of your friends.  If they scream, you win!

"You Can't Scare Me" is coming to Meta Quest 2 & 3 in Fall 2024!

Wishlist the game here: https://www.meta.com/en-us/experiences/you-cant-scare-me/6491117354320449/?utm_source=yt_anc_trailer
